title: Star Trek Phase 2 Kitumba - Episode 4x08 (HD).mp4
description:
This is the latest long awaited episode of Star Trek New Voyages/Phase II.This also is the last episode with James Cawley appearing as Captain James T. Kirk.

The script for this was originally wrote for the Star Trek Phase II that was planned in the 1970s but was never used.Wrote in 1977 for 2 episodes,it was redone for an extended episode.

Pay a visit to www.startreknewvoyages.com to check this group out.They have done excellent work.Contribute if you can.
